      • initPctCanopy

        private void initPctCanopy()
        Sets percent canopies for Density.ONE through Density.FOUR for the regional zones by setting their Range which consists of a lower and upper bounds. e.g. Colorado Plateau - Density.ONE = 0-10%, Density.TWO = 11-40%, Density.THREE= 41-70%, Density.FOUR = 71-100%

      • inPctCanopyRange

        Parameters:
        lower - lower bound
        upper - upper bound
        Returns:
        true if percent canopy is in the range lower upper inclusive
